保时捷使命 X https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/Barry Ritholtz Sun, 18 Jun 2023 15:00:17 +0000 CarsWeekend https://ritholtz.com/?p=314837 <p>保时捷 Mission X 是电动汽车不断战胜内燃机的最新一步。从 Teslas 到廉价的入门级 BYD，再到超级跑车和超级跑车，这是一个改变游戏规则的转变，就像 Dylan 第一次绑上 Stratocaster 并尽情享受时一样。 Mission X 是一款超轻型超级跑车，取代了 918 Spyder。它是…</p><p><a class="button" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/">阅读更多<i class="icon ion-arrow-right-c"></i></a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/">Porsche Mission X 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a>上。</p> ; <p><a href="https://www.porsche.com/usa/mission-x/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">保时捷 Mission X</a>是电动汽车不断战胜内燃机的最新一步。从 Teslas 到廉价的入门级<a href="https://www.byd.com/us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BYD，</a>再到超级跑车和超级跑车，这是一个改变游戏规则的转变，就像 Dylan 第一次绑上<a href="https://news.wttw.com/2018/11/20/bob-dylan-s-legendary-electric-guitar-display-chicago" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stratocaster</a>并尽情享受时一样。</p><p> Mission X 是一款超轻型超级跑车，取代了 918 Spyder。它的质量高度集中在驾驶员身后（而不是在乘客舱下方），这使得它不仅速度快而且敏捷。其 1:1 的功率/重量比使其成为有史以来最快的量产车之一，在不到 2 秒的时间内达到 0-60 MPH 的弹簧。保时捷声称它将成为纽博格林著名的北环环路上最快的合法上路车辆。该 <a href="https://www.stuttcars.com/the-porsche-mission-x-in-depth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">记录，6:35.18</a> ，目前由梅赛德斯-AMG One 保持，本质上是一种街头合法的一级方程式赛车。</p><p>一些更惊人的细节：</p><blockquote><p> – 功率：~1,480 HP（估计）<br /> – 不寻常的比例：14.8 英尺长，但只有 3.9 英尺高；<br /> – 空气阻力优于 911 GT3 RS<br /> – 1000+ 磅来自主动空气动力学的下压力；<br /> – 900 V 架构，（大约是 Taycan Turbo S 充电时间的一半）；<br /> – 驾驶员仪表、中控台和乘客的多屏幕。<br /> – 剪刀开门</p></blockquote><p>价格尚未公布，但预计 2026 年左右交付的有限生产成本将达到 7 位数。</p><p>以前的保时捷超级跑车也有类似的限制：保时捷 959（1986 年至 1993 年 300 辆）、Carrera GT（ <a href="https://www.porsche.com/stories/mobility/the-legend-of-the-porsche-carrera-gt-a-classic-sports-car-inspired-by-le-mans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1270 辆</a>）和保时捷 918 插电式混合动力车（ <a href="https://www.porsche.com/stories/innovation/how-much-is-a-porsche-918-spyder" target="_blank" rel="noopener">918 辆</a>）都是小批量生产。</p><p>如果保时捷制造了 1000 多个这样的怪物，那将是一个惊喜。</p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314838" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-250x141.jpeg 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1536x864.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314840" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="406" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg 1440w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-1024x577.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-768x433.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-250x141.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314843" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg 1035w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-768x